1. npm init
2. npm install express
3. npm install ejs (ejs is like duplicate of HTML but hum agar kisi tag mein 2+2 (div 2+ 2div)likhenge html mein toh fir
    yeh add karke nahin dega html, but ejs humein yeh kaam karke dega)

4. Setpu ejs as a view engine(see index.js file "app.set('view engine', 'ejs')")
5. create a folder name 'views' and in this folder create index.ejs file   
6. create public folder and in this folder create javascripts folder, stylesheets folder and images folder
7. in index.js, import this:- "const path = require("path");"
8.
in index.js, add this code:- "app.use(express.static(path.join(_dirname, 'public')));"